data.description: If you are looking for a home with space and room to grow, this is it! Ranch floor plan with 3BR/2BA on the main level & FINISHED TERRACE LEVEL with separate entrance and garage! Main level has hardwood floors in living space, kitchen has tile flooring, SS appliance package, and solid surface countertops. Primary bedroom has large bath with tile shower, double vanities, garden tub, and double closet space. Finished terrace level has bedroom, bathroom, living space, kitchen area, storage room and bonus area. Nice patio outback to relax and enjoy the level fenced in backyard with creek! Low maintenance with brick and vinyl exterior. Great location close to town but outside city limits. Trailwaves already set up!
